-name
-vendor

Product Variant
-product_variant_code
-name
-product type
-color
-type(slim fit, regular fit)
-size(s,l,xl)

Purchase Order
-product variant
-purchase date
-purchase price
-cgst
-sgst
-qty

Inventory
-product variant
-purchase price
-selling price
-qty
-damaged qty
-returned qty

Order
-order number
