-transaction id
-cash paid
-balance returned

Order Item(individual items in order)
-order number
-product variant
-qty(always be 1, if 4 qty purchased in this product variant, each will have separate entry)
-selling price
-cgst
-sgst
-discount %
-sold price
-status(sold, returned mismatch size, returned damaged)